	(-1532002, 'Who dares attack the steed of the Huntsman?', NULL, NULL, 'Wer wagt es Hand an das Ross des Jägers zu legen?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 9298, 6, 0, 0, 'attumen SAY_APPEAR2'),
